<bibRefCitation author="TAYLOR J. D. &amp; GLOVER E. A." box="[558,730,1424,1441]" pageId="34" pageNumber="839" pagination="281 - 338" refId="ref24590" refString="TAYLOR J. D. &amp; GLOVER E. A. 2005. - Cryptic diversity of chemosynthetic bivalves: a systematic revision of worldwide Anodontia (Mollusca: Bivalvia: Lucinidae). Systematics and Biodiversity 3 (3): 281 - 338." type="journal article" year="2005">Taylor &amp; Glover,2005</bibRefCitation>
